# Sign-in (optional). Without these, vision runs exactly as before and the
# Account card in Settings explains that sign-in isn't switched on.
#
# Get both from your Supabase project → Settings → API.
# The anon key is designed to ship in client code — it is NOT a secret.
# Row-level security is what protects each user's data.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local for local dev (.env* is gitignored).
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key
